-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><b>In the first topic, Newspaper Journalism, we have learned:</b></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ZSfPi\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Journalism is the process of creating and disseminating information on current affairs that is based on facts and backed by proof or evidence.</li><li class=\"\">The range and types of writing within newspapers and magazines are vast and varied to suit differing contexts, readership, specialisms, commercial factors, editorial control, and ownership.</li><li class=\"\">Adequate preparation is vital in carrying out a successful interview and the preparations for a telephone interview are very much the same as a face-to-face interview regarding research and planning. <br></li><li class=\"\">Broadcast news writing style differs from other writing styles, principally because, unlike most other writing, the broadcast is written for the ear, not the eye.</li><li class=\"\">The slug also includes the date, the time of the newscast, and the writer's initials.</li><li class=\"\">Some journalists combine the deductive and investigative methods;&nbsp; a journalist should always make an effort to discern between a deduction and an inference.</li><li class=\"\">It is important in news reports to make it clear where the information comes from.</li><li class=\"\">Journalists need to develop writing and reporting skills and technical and production skills, such as using video cameras and editing software.</li><li class=\"\">External microphones and input jacks are affixed to the camera body for recording audio.</li><li class=\"\">Good videographers shoot their footage in groups called sequences, collecting shots concentrated in a single visual setting.</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"LSrmc\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h4><b>Lesson Summary - Newspaper Journalism</b></h4></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"DmlWZ\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list paragraph, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"editable p-asset ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><b>In the first topic, Newspaper Journalism, we have learned:</b></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"ZSfPi\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Journalism is the process of creating and disseminating information on current affairs that is based on facts and backed by proof or evidence.</li><li class=\"\">The range and types of writing within newspapers and magazines are vast and varied to suit differing contexts, readership, specialisms, commercial factors, editorial control, and ownership.</li><li class=\"\">Adequate preparation is vital in carrying out a succ